stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Waiting : Plane added to airport

    Waiting --> Assigned : Flight assignment confirmed

    Assigned --> EnRoute : Plane cleared for take-off
    note right of Assigned
        Plane is prepared
        for departure
    end note

    EnRoute --> Landing : Destination reached
    note right of EnRoute
        Plane is actively
        flying the route
    end note

    Landing --> PostFlightCheck : Plane successfully landed
    note right of Landing
        Airport prepares
        for arrival
    end note

    PostFlightCheck --> Waiting : Plane passes inspection\n(ready for new flight)
    PostFlightCheck --> Maintenance : Maintenance required

    Maintenance --> Waiting : Repairs completed\n(plane cleared)
    Maintenance --> Disposed : Cannot be repaired

    Disposed --> [*] : Plane removed from airport